OL,3,CWho is Noel Clarke?
OL,5,FBorn in London, Noel Clarke was raised
OL,6,Fby his mother, a nurse.
OL,8,FHe studied media and took classes at
OL,9,FLondon's Actors Centre before making
OL,10,Fhis debut in the 1999 Channel 4 TV
OL,11,Fseries Metrosexuality.
OL,13,FIn 2003, he won the Most Promising
OL,14,FPerformer award at the Olivier Awards
OL,15,Ffor his performance in Where Do We
OL,16,FLive at the Royal Court Theatre, and
OL,17,Fthen significantly widened his fan
OL,18,Fbase by playing Billie Piper's
OL,19,Fboyfriend, Mickey Smith, in Doctor Who.
