OL,3,CWho is Noel Clarke?
OL,5,FHe also gained fame as Wyman Norris in
OL,6,FAuf Wiedersehen, Pet, before later
OL,7,Fwriting and starring in the acclaimed
OL,8,Ffilm trilogy Kidulthood, Adulthood and
OL,9,FBrotherhood, directing two of them.
OL,11,FHe co-founded his own production
OL,12,Fcompany, Unstoppable Entertainment, in
OL,13,F2007, which has produced films
OL,14,Fincluding Jessica Hynes's directorial
OL,15,Fdebut, The Fight, and 1010, directed
OL,16,Fby Suzi Ewing and starring Luke Evans
OL,17,Fand Kelly Reilly.
OL,19,FHe then won the Bafta rising star
OL,20,Faward in 2009, crediting the award for
OL,21,Fhis long career.
