OL,3,CWho is Noel Clarke?
OL,5,FIn 2015, Clarke's former friend Adam
OL,6,FDeacon was given a restraining order
OL,7,Ffollowing hundreds of abusive posts
OL,8,Faimed at Clarke on Instagram and
OL,9,FTwitter, after a row over the title of
OL,10,FDeacon's hit 2011 film Anuvahood.
OL,12,FIn 2018, Unstoppable Entertainment
OL,13,Fjoined forces with All3Media and
OL,14,Flaunched Unstoppable Film and
OL,15,FTelevision to expand their remit to
OL,16,Finclude television, which led to the
OL,17,Flaunch of Sky One drama Bulletproof,
OL,18,Fin which he starred prior to the
OL,19,Fallegations coming to light.
