OL,3,CWho is Noel Clarke?
OL,5,FBafta then awarded him the outstanding
OL,6,FBritish contribution to cinema prize
OL,7,Fin April 2021, but this and Clarke's
OL,8,Fmembership of the academy were
OL,9,Fsuspended after the allegations
OL,10,Fagainst him were published by the
OL,11,FGuardian.
OL,13,FClarke dropped legal action against
OL,14,Fthe academy in 2022, but launched a
OL,15,Flibel claim against Guardian News &
OL,16,FMedia (GNM) the same year.
OL,18,FDuring the High Court trial earlier
OL,19,Fthis year, Clarke appeared visibly
OL,20,Femotional as he claimed the publisher
OL,21,Fhad "smashed my life".
