OL,3,CWho is Noel Clarke?
OL,5,FHe said: "They have smashed my life
OL,6,Ffor four years with this rubbish, this
OL,7,Fnonsense. Four years."
OL,9,FHe continued: "I did not do this, I
OL,10,Fwould not do this. I have got
OL,11,Fchildren. This is not true."
OL,13,FHe later said that while he was "a
OL,14,Fflawed guy", he added: "The reason I
OL,15,Fstand here four years later is I am
OL,16,Fnot what they have branded me."
